00:12:23.630 --> 00:12:25.490
So we tried to write Isotretinoin

00:12:25.490 --> 00:12:26.980
or Accutane for this child.

00:12:26.980 --> 00:12:29.080
We did the pregnancy test, we did put her

00:12:29.080 --> 00:12:31.820
on the birth control pill
as required by the system,

00:12:31.820 --> 00:12:33.990
and we thought it might help her acne.

00:12:33.990 --> 00:12:36.660
It was repeatedly denied
by her MediCal HMO.

00:12:36.660 --> 00:12:39.660
And again, I consider this
